      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SWEET SUNDOWN (1) goes very well here starting 11 times for five wins and three minors. Below best last time at Launceston (16.71) in a Grade 5, finishing a 5 length seventh. Has the ability and should feature. HIGHGATE NELLY (6) turned in a plain performance last time when fifth at this track over 340m behind Blackpool Myer (21.36) in a Restricted WIN. Scored at her previous run. Can do much better this time. BABA'S SWIFT (2) had a tricky draw and ran well to finish second, beaten a nose, (19.35) at this track. The form out of last race has been strong. Must be included in calculations. DEWANA REJECT (4) gave nothing else a chance most recently. Big chance on that form.",
